## Dataset

This project uses the NSL-KDD dataset for network intrusion detection.

Dataset source:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/hassan06/nslkdd

Files used:
- KDDTrain+.txt
- KDDTest+.txt

The dataset is loaded directly in Google Colab using the Kaggle API.
Due to size and licensing considerations, the raw dataset is not stored in this repository.

